Lyo::OSLC
=========

This is a set of Perl modules that use the OSLC interface to interact
with Rational Team Concert and Rational ClearQuest. 

The goal of the modules is to query and update work items in Rational
Team Concert, change requests in ClearQuest, and potentially other record
types provided by other OSLC Change Management providers.

Please see the POD for the modules for additional information.

DEPENDENCIES

This is the list of direct dependencies to modules that
don't normally ship with Perl. Additional module might
be required due to dependencies that these module might have.

   REST::Client
   LWP::UserAgent
   XML::Simple
   URI
   URI::Escape
   HTTP::Cookies
   
INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

